TITLE: Episode 74 - Revenge of the Florida Men (Featuring Tho Bishop)
DESCRIPTION: This week, Jessica and I are joined by the one and only Tho Bishop. We talk how much better it is in Florida, how Trump's legacy, democracy, leading by example, and how lame the LP is. Join us, nerds.
